  <brief_title>Electrogastrography in Small for Gestational Age Preterm Infants</brief_title>
  <official_title>Electrogastrography in Small for Gestational Age Preterm Infants Compared to Appropriate for Gestational Age Infants</official_title>
  <sponsors>
